parameters:
\SE[33]I think it's urgent, so... I apologize for not
knocking...!

\SE[5]Huh... Did you not wake up...? I think there was a
pretty loud noise... \SE[100]Could it be that I was just
half asleep...?

\SE[50]If that's the case, I wouldn't like it... \!\SE[95]I
entered the lady's room without even knocking, so I might
get arrested for Maiden Trespassing Crime...
\SE[22]Ah, she's mumbling... Luna is cute like this too...

\SE[116]N-No! This is not the time to be saying that...!
\SE[95]D-Did you use magic while half asleep...!!?

\SE[92]Is it really okay to leave this alone!? It seems to
be in a really dangerous state...!!??

\SE[116]H-Hii...!? \.That thing is really bad news!
\!\SE[33]It's the one that has blown away numerous
formidable enemies...!

\SE[114]If this continues, it will be the end...! \SE[33]The
Indiscriminate Quadruple Magic will begin...!!
\SE[99]That just now... It feels like déjà vu...

\SE[102]She really has become a futanari... I can tell even
from her clothes, she has an impressive one...

\SE[57]N-No... I'm not thinking anything weird...?
\SE[58]I-I'm not even a little bit interested in anything
lewd... I-I'm not a lewd girl or anything...

\SE[40]N-No, this is bad...! \.The situation hasn't been
resolved at all!!

\SE[99]Just because Luna grew a penis, it doesn't mean the
situation has been resolved at all... \SE[100]If this
continues, it might become a serious problem...

\SE[22]Ehehe... This isn't the time to be getting all lovey-
dovey...!

\SE[9]I'm sure Luna is backed up... \!\SE[100]They say that
the quality of sleep decreases when you have stress, it's
common knowledge in the city after all...

\SE[57]I-if it's true that she's accumulating lewd stress,
as her lover, I also have a responsibility... \SE[58]I have
an obligation to help her release it, right...

\SE[102]Alright, I'll do something about it...! I'll find a
way to calm Luna's penis down! \SE[100]As your lover,
I'll...!!

\SE[57]I-I don't have any interest in lewd things... I-I
only do it because it's necessary...!
